<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="22">{\an8}（他这样说了）</font>

118
00:08:58,500 --> 00:08:59,500
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="22">{\an8}（真亏大家坚持到现在）</font>

119
00:08:59,500 --> 00:09:00,120
