125
00:09:22,520 --> 00:09:24,790
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">不是那种东西  而是实际的…</font>

126
00:09:25,000 --> 00:09:30,840
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">没错「应该不是那种东西」我也会这么想的</font>

127
00:09:31,480 --> 00:09:32,610
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">…一般来说的话</font>

128
00:09:33,560 --> 00:09:35,460
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">但是  阿良良木君</font>

129
00:09:35,760 --> 00:09:39,780
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">班长小妹可不正常  那孩子相当不妙的</font>

